explorer.ui
Class EditUI

java.lang.Object
  explorer.ui.EditUI
public class EditUI
extends java.lang.Object

EditUI is responsible for setting up the view part of the menu- and tool-bar. The "Clear attributes" and "Clear command" items are only enabled when isAdmin is true.
